	<h1 class="title">「酸汤鱼经济学」为什么中国足球队的水平越来越低？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3891/small/3891.jpg?1418027288" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">酸汤鱼 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-11 06:17:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14752/medium/14752.jpg?1441867391" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="14752" data-title="《「酸汤鱼经济学」为什么中国足球队的水平越来越低？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/14752/medium/14752.jpg?1441867391" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/14752.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
